WEBVTT

00:00:00.669 --> 00:00:02.730
Imagine you're on a shopping trip.

00:00:02.754 --> 00:00:06.239
You've been looking
for a luxury-line dinnerware set

00:00:06.263 --> 00:00:08.016
to add to your kitchen collection.

00:00:08.579 --> 00:00:09.730
As it turns out,

00:00:09.754 --> 00:00:12.511
your local department store
has announced a sale

00:00:12.535 --> 00:00:15.004
on the very set you've been looking for,

00:00:15.028 --> 00:00:19.378
so you rush to the store
to find a 24-piece set on sale.

00:00:20.581 --> 00:00:23.541
Eight dinner plates,
all in good condition;

00:00:23.565 --> 00:00:26.604
eight soup and salad bowls,
all in good condition;

00:00:26.628 --> 00:00:29.588
and eight dessert plates,
all in good condition.